name: Caffeine Sketches    42pages
description:
Caffeine Sketches
This book owes its genesis to caffeine.
I’ve consumed a lot of it over the years. Hours, weeks, months – what seems like a lifetime – has been spent sitting in cafes reading, writing, drawing and observing.
What you see here is a small caffeinated collection of visual diary pages, a recollection of the past three years of my life.
These are not finished works, they’re simply rough caffeine sketches, the results of long hours spent drinking coffee in cafes all across the world.
Enjoy.
